snippet.title: Olympic Winter Games - Lillehammer' 94 (Mega Drive/Genesis) - Longplay
snippet.description:
Winter Olympics (ウィンターオリンピック) or Winter Olympics: Lillehammer '94 and known as Winter Olympic Games in North America, is a Sega Mega Drive, Sega Master System and Sega Game Gear sports game that ties in with the 1994 Winter Olympic Games held at Lillehammer, Norway.

Let's Play By Madmatty

#Longplay #SegaMD2
